---
description: BootstrapBlazor AI Skill discovery rules
alwaysApply: true
---

Before generating BootstrapBlazor component code, read `skill-index.json`.

Read order:

1. Current component source in `src/BootstrapBlazor/Components/<ComponentName>`.
2. Official Sample from the index when it exists.
3. Component Skill from the index when it exists.

If a Sample exists, prefer the Sample over Skill examples. If no Sample exists, use the Skill examples after validating the current source.

Do not guess parameters, events, obsolete APIs, or historical BootstrapBlazor behavior.
